                "description": "High-temperature-resistant nitrile rubber membrane containing pre-pressurized inert gas."
              },
              {
                "name": "Pressure Housing",
                "type": "Structural Component",
                "description": "Cylindrical alloy housing with corrosion-resistant coating to withstand high-pressure cycling."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "name": "Pressure Relief Valve",
